**Stash-pop sanity check (regression-target verification):**

Reverted four load-bearing pieces (classifyPersona stale-default fallback, setUserDefaultLeague membership gate, touchUserDefaultLeague membership gate, HomepageRouter single→redirect dispatch) — 4 of 57 tests fail on the broken state. Restored after verification:

- `classifyPersona — STALE defaultLeagueId fallback`
- `touchUserDefaultLeague — requires APPROVED + current PLM in THIS league`
- `setUserDefaultLeague — rejects when user has no APPROVED PLM`
- (HomepageRouter redirect-on-single — caught by structural pin)

